<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <%- include("head.ejs") %>
<head>
  <title>Edmonton Chess Club</title>
  <style>
    /* CSS Styling */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f2f2f2;
      margin: 0;
    }
    
    .home_container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    
    .home_menu {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    .home_menu li {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: 10px;
    }
    
    .home_menu li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      background-color: #333;
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 5px;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .home_menu li a:hover {
      background-color: #555;
    }
    
    .home_content {
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    
    .home_content h2 {
      margin-top: 30px;
      color: #555;
    }
    
    .home_content p {
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .home_content ol {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .home_content ol li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    
    .home_footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #888;
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #ccc;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="home_container">
    
    <nav class="home_menu">
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/tournaments">Tournaments</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Classes</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Membership</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
    
    <section class="home_content">
      <h2>About Us</h2>
      <p>The Edmonton Chess Club is a vibrant and inclusive community for chess enthusiasts of all ages and skill levels. We aim to promote the game of chess, foster a spirit of friendly competition, and provide a platform for players to improve their skills and engage in enjoyable chess-related activities.</p>
      
      <h2>Club Activities</h2>
      <ol>
        <li>Regular Tournaments: Participate in our frequent tournaments and test your skills against other players in the community. We organize various formats, including classical, rapid, blitz, and online tournaments.</li>
        <li>Chess Classes: Enhance your chess knowledge and skills by joining our chess classes.</li>
      </ol>
      
      <h2>Membership Benefits</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access to exclusive tournaments and events</li>
        <li>Discounted rates for chess classes and workshops</li>
        <li>Opportunity to connect and learn from fellow chess enthusiasts</li>
        <li>Access to a chess library with a wide range of resources</li>
        <li>Regular updates on upcoming chess events and activities</li>
      </ul>
      
      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>If you have any questions or would like to get in touch with us, please use the contact information below:</p>
      
      <p>Email: info@edmontonchessclub.com</p>
      <p>Phone: +1 123-456-7890</p>
    </section>
    
    
  </div>
</body>
<%- include("footer.ejs") %>
</html>
